title: [Good Fences]
description: Uneven flooring with a decided downward slant holds dozens of rickety shelves crammed with dust-covered trinkets from numerous ports of call.  A glass-fronted countertop may once have been designed to showcase wares, but its current smudged and saltstained existence reveals only shadowy outlines of items in its depths.  Sitting on top of the countertop is a small sign propped up by a rusty bell that reads, "Ring for Service."
